  95401 (cross road Stony Point Road). Arrive by 6:15pm.\n\n## **Santa Rosa
  Toastmasters 182 helps members improve their public speaking and leadersh
 ip skills. Meetings are lively and supportive where each individual feels 
 at ease and thrives. We’re a friendly and diverse group with the motto\,
  “We Make Public Speaking Fun!”**
